articles.title: West Ham 2-0 Rapid Vienna: Declan Rice, Said Benrahma score to give Hammers second win in Europa League group - Sky Sports
articles.description: Declan Rice and Said Benrahma capped the London Stadium's first home game in a European finals with the goals in West Ham's 2-0 victory over Rapid Vienna.
